metamagic.notes:
The Adept can take a Free action, buying hits on a (IG + Related Combat Skill) [Related Combat Skill] test, to enhance an attack.

Related Combat Skills:
* Any Combat Active skills in the same skill group are related;
* Heavy Weapons, Spray Weapons, and Directed Energy count as related;
* Monofilament Weapons, Throwing Weapons, and Archery count as related;
* For Gunnery, the combat skill that the weapon normally uses counts as related;
* For combat use of Gymnastics (via Clinch), Unarmed Combat counts as related.
